description: Under normal market conditions, the fund will seek its investment objective by investing at least 80% of its assets in a portfolio comprised of fixed income securities, debt instruments, derivatives, equity securities of any type acquired in reorganizations of issuers of fixed income securities or debt instruments ("work out securities"), non-convertible preferred securities, warrants, cash and cash equivalents, foreign currencies, and exchange-traded funds ("ETFs") that provide exposure to these investments.
name: Western Asset Total Return ETF
